reviewText: kool cheese to watch and dvd came in good shape, considering this is an old light porno. Good shots of Dana Plato.

Great little comedy produced & directed by veteran filmmaker Eric Louzil who also directed the "Class of Nuke'Em High" films.  This was one of Dana Plato's last films.  DanaPlato was the teenage star of the very popular TV Series "Different Strokes".  The world famous porn actor Ron Jeremy is also in the film.  The film was shot in Miami, Florida and the locations are very pretty.  The story revolves around the annual "Bikini Beach Bed Race" which is a charity event that has been somewhat toned down as one of the girls fell off one of the beds during a race.
